						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone in front of the temple of Durgā-Paramēs11vari.</hi></p>						

						<p>Siṁghaṇa—A.D. 1236.</p>						

						<p>This inscription is dated in the <hi rend="bold">26th year</hi> of the reign of <hi rend="bold">Siṁghaṇadēva, Manmatha, Phālguṇa ba 10, Tuesday,</hi> corresponding <hi rend="bold">to A.D. 1236, March 4, Tuesday.</hi> It States that when <hi rend="bold">Pāṇḍiyadēva</hi> attacked <hi rend="bold">Ajaḍi, Karageya Sōvabōva</hi> died after killing the enemies.</p>						

						</summary>
